      <scopecontent id="ref4">
         <head>Description of the Material</head>
         <p>Includes a geologic map of Kansas, topographic maps of Utah, field notes about a Cambrian carpoid locality in Utah, field notes from Hawaii and Utah (from a collecting trip with Llyod, Val and Glade Gunther, and Tom and Brian Whitely), and assorted slides.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
